the ruinous condition of the factory, which has required him to rent a house from William Bruce.</abstract><typeOfResource>text</typeOfResource><genre type="class">Letter</genre><accessCondition type="Use and reproduction" xlink:href="http://www.qdl.qa/en/archive/81055/vdc_100075534085.0x0000e0#share">Open Government Licence</accessCondition></mods>	</en_metadata>
